stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> Generated: Daily batch job
    Generated --> SentToGateway
    SentToGateway --> Delivered: Success (200 OK)
    SentToGateway --> Retrying: Failure (5xx)
    Retrying --> SentToGateway: Retry (max 3x)
    Retrying --> Failed: Max retries exceeded
    Delivered --> [*]
    Failed --> [*]
